reviewText: These dvds are incredible and have made me stop going home to watch tv.  Im about a week in and already have completed three puppets.  Building my set this week.

Awesome guide, I made an awesome puppet. Very easy to follow. Its a recording of an online class the brothers did which i was not expecting but still very good. They ramble a lot during the video but the rambling are interesting and coming from pretty experienced guys so you learn a lot that would other wise be learned through trial and error.
